## Module 5: TypeScript with React for Type Safety

Type safety is one of the most powerful features TypeScript brings to React development. By integrating TypeScript with React, you can catch errors during development, improve code maintainability, and create more robust applications. This module will guide you through setting up TypeScript in a React project, typing React components, props, hooks, and handling complex types and generics.

